class_notes: This section is for DABSN semester 2 students only.
course_description: Students examine reproductive health and maternal nursing care of women across the continuum from preconception, antepartum, intra-partum, through postpartum. A global perspective frames health promotion and disease prevention emphasizing maternal-newborn dyads and their families.
